3
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:02,200
acabo encontrando

4
00:00:02,200 --> 00:00:02,800
algo.

5
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:03,120
Y lo que

6
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:03,960
mas os va

7
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:04,600
