33
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:23,880
Se degrada.

34
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:24,400
En horas.

35
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:24,760
El sol

36
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,160
